This place has great food for a great price.  We order the specialty spaghetti which was spinach pasta with veggies and chicken with a delicious butter sauce.  We also ordered some empanadas which were delicious.  My mom makes great crane empanadas since we are from Paraguay and my boyfriend said he carne ones were similar to my mom's.  I tried the jamón, queso,and olives, and it was really good.  Every meal comes with bread, a drink,and dessert.  I got the tiramisu and my boyfriend got the cheesecake.  Both were really good.  I recommend coming here.  Great food for a really good price!
